+++ b/README.md
@@ -3,6 +3,10 @@
 `ledgerlite` is a deliberately small invoice and payment service used by the
 Garfield coordinator benchmark. It has no network or service dependencies.
 
+Payment creation accepts an optional `Idempotency-Key`. Repeating the same key
+and payload within an account returns the original payment; changing the
+payload returns the documented conflict response.
+
 ## Validation
 
 Run the aggregate validation entry point from the repository root:
